    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2399370/extras/59206eca8d8364e9437f36379d01063a.poster.avif?t=1709030761\" width=604 height=130 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2399370/extras/59206eca8d8364e9437f36379d01063a.webm?t=1709030761\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2399370/extras/59206eca8d8364e9437f36379d01063a.mp4?t=1709030761\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >WHOLESOME MINIGAMES / CUTE COMEDY ADVENTURE </h2><br><i>You control Slippy the square, soaking, frog as he travels the land solving peoples problems by entering their mind mini games.</i><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2399370/extras/7e4218ddac2e1651b411fc953d99fb44.poster.avif?t=1709030761\" width=604 height=146 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2399370/extras/7e4218ddac2e1651b411fc953d99fb44.webm?t=1709030761\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2399370/extras/7e4218ddac2e1651b411fc953d99fb44.mp4?t=1709030761\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Gameplay</strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> MIND MINI GAMES - you gotta hop in their heads and fix their problems<br></li><li> FRIENDS - Slippy makes, like, a million friends on the way<br></li><li> FBI WORK - Slippy is stepping in for the FBI on this job, so the stakes are pretty high<br></li><li> FROGS - money back guarantee if there isn't at least one frog in your game<br></li><li> PARTY - after completing his job, SLIPPY attends a rad party</li></ul><br><strong>Short Game</strong><br>40 hour games? YAWN - Slippy is short and jam packed with stuff to do.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2399370/extras/e2a0d08075581bafb487b0a5b10643c6.poster.avif?t=1709030761\" width=600 height=154 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2399370/extras/e2a0d08075581bafb487b0a5b10643c6.webm?t=1709030761\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2399370/extras/e2a0d08075581bafb487b0a5b10643c6.mp4?t=1709030761\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Interactive</strong><br>SLIPPY is a fully interactable piece of software known as a computer game.<br><br><br><strong>Thank you for playing my game!</strong><br>I've loved making this game so thank you for checking it out :D &lt;3<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2399370/extras/10870785902c7954cfdd3b1441301ad9.poster.avif?t=1709030761\" width=598 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2399370/extras/10870785902c7954cfdd3b1441301ad9.webm?t=1709030761\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2399370/extras/10870785902c7954cfdd3b1441301ad9.mp4?t=1709030761\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
